Field CaseID Before //add code here CALL IllnessCheck End-Before End-Field
Field DOB After // Assigns the difference in years between the value entered into DOB and the value // entered into DateOfInterview to the AGE field. This acts as an automatic age // calculator during data entry. ASSIGN AGE = YEARS(DOB, DateofInterview) End-After End-Field
Field GetCoordinates Click GEOCODE PatientAddress, Latitude, Longitude End-Click End-Field
Field OnsetDate After ASSIGN OnsetWeek = EPIWEEK(OnsetDate) End-After End-Field

Field FeverTemp After // if the fever temperature field has been filled in and the fever checkbox is unchecked, // prompt the user that there might be a problem. IF NOT FeverTemp = (.)
